videos.description: Kameron Chatman hits a 3 from the corner with .02 seconds left in the game to lift Michigan to a 72-69 win over top-seeded Indiana in the Big Ten Tournament quarterfinal.
videos.headline: Chatman's buzzer-beating 3 the difference for Michigan
